high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter on the right.
Pick up the knife to the right of the bread.
Turn and walk to the sink on the other side of the room.
Place the knife in the sink in front of the sharp knife.
Turn around and walk back to the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter to the left of the lettuce.
Turn and walk back over to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink behind the wine glass.
anns.task_desc: To move two knives to the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn right to the counter to the right of the black stool. Go to the counter.
Take the knife on the right of the bread from the counter.
Turn around, go forward a step, turn left, go forward, when the door is to the right turn left, go forward to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn around, go forward to the door, turn right, go forward to the wall, turn right, go forward to the black stool.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn around, go forward a step, turn left, go forward, when the door is to the right turn left, go forward to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two knives in a sink.

high_descs: Go to the kitchen island
Pick up the butterknife from the kitchen island
Go to the sink
Place the butterknife in the sink
Go to the kitchen island
Pick up another butterknife from the kitchen island
Go to the sink
Put the butterknife in the sink
anns.task_desc: Move two butterknives into a sink
